    "text": "Enable Accessibility\nBetter Health, Brighter Future\nNewsroom\nCareers\nInvestors\nPatients\nHCPs\nWORLDWIDE\nWHO WE ARE\n\nWHAT WE DO\nOUR STORIES\nCORPORATE RESPONSIBILITY\nApproved for Use in European Union\nLEARN MORE\nWelcome to the Global\nCorporate Website for Takeda\nIf you are looking for specific information,\nplease visit our country/region website. \n \n\n        SELECT A COUNTRY OR REGION SITE\nAccess to Medicine 2022 Progress Report\nLEARN MORE\nEarnings announcement for the 2nd quarter FY2022 (Oct 27, 2022)\nLEARN MORE\nRECENT NEWS\nSTOCK PRICE\nJAN 5, 2023\nTakeda Announces Favorable Phase 3 Safety and Efficacy Results of TAK-755 as Compared to Standard of Care in Congenital Thrombotic Thrombocytopenic Purpura (cTTP)\nGO TO NEWSROOM\n\n\n\nTopics\n2022 Annual Integrated Report\nLEARN MORE\nAndy Plump discusses maintaining trust in science.\nLEARN MORE\nOur Stories\nLEARN MORE\nCorporate Responsibility\nLEARN MORE\nInformation\n41st Annual J.P. Morgan Healthcare Conference (4:30pm – 5:10pm PST on January 9, 2023)\nEarnings announcement for the 2nd quarter FY2022 (October 27, 2022)\nWebcast for Investors, Analysts and Media, 6:30pm-8:00pm JST (Presentation and Q&A Session)\n146th Ordinary General Meeting of Shareholders (June 29, 2022)\nInformation for US Patients Regarding the NATPARA Recall in the US\nADS Helpline\n  Sign up for emails from Takeda\nStay up to date on financial results, corporate milestones and learn how Takeda is delivering on our commitment to patients, our people and the planet.\nSUBSCRIBE\nTERMS OF USE TAKEDA PRIVACY NOTICE COOKIE POLICY ACCESSIBILITY STATEMENT\nCopyright 1995-2023 Takeda Pharmaceutical Company Limited. All rights reserved.\nConnect with us:\nWORLDWIDE\nBy clicking “Accept All Cookies”, you agree to the storing of cookies on your device to enhance site navigation, analyze site usage, and assist in our marketing efforts. Cookie Policy\nCookies Settings Reject All Accept All Cookies",
